\c 2
\s Vapristi vanotukwa naJehovha
\p
\v 1 Zvino ikozvino, vapristi, murairo uyu ndewenyu.
\v 2 Kana musingateereri, uye kana mukasaisa mumoyo, kupa rukudzo kuzita rangu, anoreva Jehovha wehondo, ndatuma chakatukwa kurwisana nemwi, uye ndatuka maropafadzo enyu, hongu, ndazvituka, nokuti hamuzviisi mumoyo.
\v 3 Tarirai, ndichaodza chizvarwa chenyu, nekumwaya ndove pazviso zvenyu, ndove yemabiko enyu, uye ndichakubvisai pamwe nayo.
\v 4 Zvino muchaziva kuti ndakutumirai murairo uyu, kuti sungano yangu ive naRevhi, anoreva Jehovha wehondo.
\v 5 Sungano yangu navo yaiva kwaari upenyu nerugare, uye ndakavapa kutya kwavakanditya nako, uye vakatya pamberi pezita rangu.
\v 6 Murairo wechokwadi waiva mumuromo make, uye uipi hauna kuwanikwa pamiromo yake, wakafamba neni murugare nemukururama, uye wakatendeusa vazhinji kubva pauipi.
\v 7 Nokuti miromo yemupristi inochengetedza ruzivo, uye murairo vakatsvaka pamuromo wake, nokuti iye mutumwa waJehovha wehondo.
\v 8 Asi imwi makatsauka kubva panzira; makagumbusa vazhinji pamurairo; makasvibisa sungano yaRevhi, anoreva Jehovha wehondo.
\v 9 Naizvozvo ndakakuitai vanozvidzwa nevari pasi pamberi pevanhu vese sezvamusina kuchengeta nzira dzangu, asi makagamuchira zviso pamurairo.
\p
\v 10 Isu tose hatina baba vamwe here? Mwari umwe haana kutisika here? Sei tichiitirana neunyengeri umwe kune wekwake, nekusvibisa sungano yemadzibaba edu?
\v 11 Judha wakaita neunyengeri, uye kwakaitwa chinyangadzo kwaIsraeri nemuJerusarema; nokuti Judha wakasvibisa utsvene hwaJehovha hwaaida, wakaroora mukunda wavamwari vatorwa.
\v 12 Zvino Jehovha achagura munhu anoita izvi, mudzidzisi nemudzidzi, kubva mumatende aJakove, neuyo anoswededza chibairo kuna Jehovha wehondo.
\v 13 Zvino izvi wazviita rwechipiri, uchifukidza nemisodzi aritari yaJehovha nekuchema nekugomera, nokuti hakuchina kutendeukira kuchibairo, kana kugamuchira chinhu chipi chinofadza kubva muruoko rwenyu.
\p
\v 14 Zvakadaro munoti: Nemhaka yei? Nekuda kwekuti Jehovha wanga ari chapupu pako nemukadzi weujaya hwako, iye wawakaitira nekunyengera, zvakadaro ari shamwari yako, uye mukadzi wesungano yako.
\v 15 Haana kuita umwe here? Zvakadaro ane mweya wakasara. Zvino nemhaka yei ari umwe? Kuti atsvage chizvarwa chinotya Mwari. Naizvozvo chenjerera mweya wako, uye usarega umwe achibata neunyengeri kumukadzi weujaya hwako.
\v 16 Nokuti ndinovenga kuramba\add na\add*, anoreva Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri. Nokuti umwe anofukidza mhirizhonga nenguvo yake, anoreva Jehovha wehondo. Naizvozvo chenjerai mweya yenyu, kuti musaita nekunyengera.
\p
\v 17 Makanetesa Jehovha nemashoko enyu. Zvakadaro munoti: Takanetesa pane zvipi? Pamunoti: Umwe neumwe anoita zvakaipa wakanaka pamberi paJehovha, uye munovafarira; kana: Aripi Mwari wemutongo?